favorite subject as well.

823
00:44:11,540 --> 00:44:13,119
I'm afraid he'll keep an eye
on your every move.

824
00:44:13,460 --> 00:44:14,659
You might not be able to act.

825
00:44:15,739 --> 00:44:17,360
I guess there's no choice.

826
00:44:18,059 --> 00:44:19,179
His Majesty would never let us

827
