838
00:44:48,099 --> 00:44:49,040
Remember to wear thicker clothing.

839
00:44:49,520 --> 00:44:50,000
Yes, Your Lordship.

840
00:44:50,679 --> 00:44:51,420
You guys as well.

841
00:44:55,800 --> 00:44:56,360
Shaojun.

842
00:44:57,940 --> 00:44:59,139
Sanlang, thank you for joining us.

843
00:44:59,559 --> 00:45:00,619
Sanlang, if you don't mind,

844
00:45:00,940 --> 00:45:01,860
you may stay at

845
00:45:01,860 --> 00:45:03,079
Changfeng Estate with us
when we arrive at Nanling.

846
00:45:03,340 --> 00:45:04,300
It'll also save you from trouble.

847
00:45:05,380 --> 00:45:06,320
If so, I won't stay on ceremony, then.

848
00:45:07,599 --> 00:45:09,000
Sanlang, are you only taking
Deputy Envoy Yi with you?

849
00:45:09,960 --> 00:45:12,960
Shaojun, I was the one
who wanted to join you on your trip.

850
00:45:13,500 --> 00:45:14,759
